-- Piramal Healthcare Is in Talks to Buy 10 Percent Stake in Super Religare
-- Adi Narayan
-- 2010-07-14T03:48:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/piramal-healthcare-is-in-talks-to-buy-10-percent-stake-in-super-religare.html

          
          
             Piramal Healthcare Ltd. is in talks
to buy 10 percent of Super Religare Laboratories Ltd., said
Gopal Vaidyanathan, director of strategy at Super Religare, in a
phone interview. The companies are expected to decide on the
stake purchase by tomorrow, he said.  
